{"tid":1316275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正名!! 咪撚叫佢哋警察，嗰班係「自稱警員嘅恐佈分子」","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:58:29.000Z","uid":87985,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53a4c67f8167d3e1546a1e435086eabcc0c0e241","tid":1316275,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"又冇委任證又著唔齊裝，仲好意思話自己係警察<br />\n<br />\n身為一個良好香港市民一早睇得穿呢班人係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恐怖分子</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以今日喺沙田某商場入面嘅市民，相當英勇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">制服咗一班恐怖分子，協助香港警察拘捕疑犯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇人打過警察，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">市民淨係對一班冒認警察嘅恐怖分子行使拘捕權</span></span>"},{"pid":"2a2d5e78fed8dae3eaffb578efce56eb518b7b27","tid":1316275,"uid":24897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"7月14晚一批懷疑冒充香港警察嘅恐怖分子衝入沙田新城市廣場，現場市民英勇抗敵，成功制服一名疑似恐怖分子。<br />\n該批人士穿着整套香港警察防暴裝備，但沒有任內委任証，更用上反光膠紙、反光鏡遮蔽樣貌。於突然衝入新城市廣場毆打平民，製造混亂。一批市民聯手制服其中一名恐怖分子"},{"pid":"29e21edc023d7bb190f5c98186fcdd2d8caa5223","tid":1316275,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:48:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55123c74ab21e5b0d90720e180fd89b1b21afc1c","tid":1316275,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"市民合力制服恐怖份子"},{"pid":"d3b4cba822989c454be45be42ea604c1523c74b0","tid":1316275,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"太激動所以禁錯負皮sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e060a826b41e5f6935b59f210073fa7b51ac375","tid":1316275,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"有啲人係到扮警察<br />\n係到亂打